highlights.text: “爱人错过 - 伴奏” by 胖虎 is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #92.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 160 days straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “KHÔNG ĐAU NỮA RỒI” is the highest at #3.
“Prokofiev: Romeo and Juliet, Op. 64, Act 1: Dance of the Knights” by Sergei Prokofiev, André Previn, and London Symphony Orchestra is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 18 spots at #60.
